'''2015年美國網球公開賽'''（2015 US Open）是第135屆[[美國網球公開賽|美國網球公開賽]]，在[[美國網球協會比莉·珍·金網球中心|美國網球協會比莉·珍·金網球中心]]舉行。本屆賽事的男子單打冠軍是[[諾瓦克·喬科維奇|諾瓦克·喬科維奇]]，女子單打冠軍是[[弗拉維婭·佩內塔|弗拉維婭·佩內塔]]。這一屆美國網球公開賽在美國國內的轉播商是ESPN<ref name=aa-espnfrenchopen>{{cite web|title=ESPN drops the French Open, NBCSN could step in|url=http://awfulannouncing.com/2015/espn-drops-the-french-open-nbcsn-could-step-in.html|website=Awful Announcing|accessdate=3 August 2015|archive-date=2016-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160629084742/http://awfulannouncing.com/2015/espn-drops-the-french-open-nbcsn-could-step-in.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=ESPN to Gain Full Rights to U.S. Open in 2015|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/05/17/sports/tennis/ending-an-era-the-us-open-will-move-to-espn.html?_r=0|accessdate=12 September 2015|work=The New York Times|archive-date=2015-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150415075906/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/05/17/sports/tennis/ending-an-era-the-us-open-will-move-to-espn.html?_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

